The change from the heart system to the energy system was a very bad decision from the duolingo development team. The Duolingo I used to know was an application that facilitated foreign language learning for us users so that we could learn foreign languages with easy access. However, unfortunately it seems that now Duolingo is chasing wealth too much, forcing everyone for paid subscriptions.
